    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\r\n\r\nThere is no official suggestion to set WSL clipboard in lua format.\r\n\r\nMy suggestion is to add\r\n\r\n```\r\nvim.opt.clipboard = {\r\n    name = \"WslClipboard\",\r\n    copy = {\r\n        ['+'] = \"clip.exe\",\r\n        ['*'] = \"clip.exe\"\r\n    },\r\n    paste = {\r\n        ['+'] = 'powershell.exe -c [Console]::Out.Write($(Get-Clipboard -Raw).tostring().replace(\"`r\", \"\"))',\r\n        ['*'] = 'powershell.exe -c [Console]::Out.Write($(Get-Clipboard -Raw).tostring().replace(\"`r\", \"\"))'\r\n    },\r\n    cache_enabled = 0\r\n}\r\n```\r\nto documentation and buildin help.\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2023-10-20T11:15:20Z",
