            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "1. That is actually incorrect, it should be `vim.g.clipboard`.\r\n2. The relevant information is already in `:h clipboard-wsl`; I don't think we should give every single code example twice (once in Vimscript, once in Lua) if the translation is straightforward (as in this case, if you've read `:h lua-guide` -- which is considered required reading).",
